name: NEW LIFE
description:
Insights from the Dreaming Pool - Physical change, a physical shift, a change of circumstances. 

Something from outside is causing a shift inside of you. Or a major shift on the inside will initiate physical change in the world. This image represents a physical change in circumstances how ever small or big, there is something coming your way. The thing about pregnancy is that you know sooner or later something is coming out. There will be a change. A baby will be born. You don’t know how it will go, you don’t know the ease or the difficulty that will be present, and when will it happen?
     
That magic time comes when all is ready, the waters break and the baby and you begin the contractions. A lot has gone in to get to this point, a lot has been growing beneath and within for you to be ready. There are many unseen reasons for why we are where we are especially if you want your life to be different than it is.  This card is indicating that the magic time has come for whatever it is you seek, whatever change it is you desire, hold on and don't forget to breathe...

The Dreaming Pool Oracle is a collaboration between artists Maia Mellier 🕸 🕷 (@maiamellier) & AEVIN (@aevin_io)
